    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently, and every feature, from the advanced electronics to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by authorized dealers.",
