    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine suffers from significant mechanical wear, including noticeable leaks and low compression, meaning it will likely require a full rebuild to be reliable. The body shows its age with several dents and areas of surface rust, while the interior has significant tearing and needs a complete overhaul. It is not currently in roadworthy condition, but it offers a solid foundation for someone looking for a major restoration project.",
