      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which stands as a testament to engineering excellence and prudent ownership. This specimen has been thoroughly vetted to ensure optimal mechanical performance and aesthetic integrity. The cabin remains refined, and the exterior retains a polished, distinguished presence. For the discerning driver seeking a harmonious blend of reliability and prestige, this automobile offers a superior ownership proposition. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional vehicle firsthand.",
      "price": 34850.0,
